      "description": "bitHuman SDK — real-time on-device AI avatar runtime for iOS, iPadOS, Android, macOS, and Linux. Private, low-latency lip-sync compositing for interactive conversational agents on-device or on-edge. Sub-50 ms turn latency, offline-capable, self-hosted. Python, Swift, Kotlin, and Rust CLI shipped from one libessence engine.",
